cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC

The paper deals with wireless access and distributed MIMO optimization in a large network, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). However, since the focus is primarily on wireless access and MIMO optimization, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories, followed by cs.SY, cs.MM, and cs.DC.
